title: Coaching Search Update on Giants, Browns and Panthers (Football 1/7)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Jason La Canfora to break down the head coaching openings around the NFL and offer updates on their ongoing searches. The guys discuss the vacancies for the Giants (2:30), Browns (12:30) and Panthers (25:30) before analyzing Tom Brady's future following the Patriots Wild Card exit against the Titans (31:00).
